/CLAUDE.md
/PROJECT_LOG.md
/PROJECT_LOG_archive.md

# --- Credentials / secrets (defense in depth; never upload) ---
*.params
*.env
.env
*secret*
*credential*
*.key
*token*

# --- Editor / OS / language noise ---
.Rhistory
.RData
.Rproj.user/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.log
.ipynb_checkpoints/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
